How do you feel, Ji Won?

30
00:01:59,021 --> 00:02:00,790
Last time, I said Seo Yoon should wait...

31
00:02:00,791 --> 00:02:02,520
as she would get a chance...

32
00:02:02,521 --> 00:02:03,791
in the last quarter.

33
00:02:04,191 --> 00:02:05,191
Here it is.

34
00:02:05,192 --> 00:02:06,590
- I see.
- It's her chance.

35
00:02:06,591 --> 00:02:08,060
What about the Late-night Date?

36
00:02:08,061 --> 00:02:10,330
- Does it not matter?
- No, it doesn't.

37
00:02:10,331 --> 00:02:12,001
