- Yes.

63
00:03:08,321 --> 00:03:09,881
- I'm jealous.
- Either summer or fall.

64
00:03:09,991 --> 00:03:11,260
- Got it.
- Gosh.

65
00:03:11,261 --> 00:03:12,991
