- Yes.

72
00:03:26,172 --> 00:03:27,440
- What's IRL?
- What is that?

73
00:03:27,441 --> 00:03:29,270
- Real-life couple.
- Real-life couple.

74
00:03:29,271 --> 00:03:31,110
