103
00:04:31,471 --> 00:04:33,241
What do you like, Yoon Hoo?

104
00:04:33,741 --> 00:04:36,511
Me? I...

105
00:04:37,181 --> 00:04:39,211
I like going on foodie dates.

106
00:04:39,381 --> 00:04:41,010
- What about you?
- Same here.

107
00:04:41,011 --> 00:04:42,781
- Really?
- Yes.

108
00:04:43,651 --> 00:04:46,621
By the way, you're really pretty.

109
00:04:47,751 --> 00:04:50,991
