- Yes.

134
00:05:59,691 --> 00:06:00,691
Yes, apples.

135
00:06:01,391 --> 00:06:02,991
- Would you like some apples?
- Yes.

136
00:06:03,901 --> 00:06:04,931
Thank you.

137
00:06:05,061 --> 00:06:06,231
This must be that.

138
00:06:06,431 --> 00:06:08,630
- I love ricotta cheese.
- Okay, you can have everything.

139
00:06:08,631 --> 00:06:09,870
Do you? No, it's okay.

140
00:06:09,871 --> 00:06:11,801
You should try some too.

141
00:06:11,841 --> 00:06:13,001
- I'm okay.
- Come on.

142
00:06:13,241 --> 00:06:14,710
(Picking out the ingredients Yu Bin likes)

143
00:06:14,711 --> 00:06:15,741
Here.

144
00:06:17,011 --> 00:06:18,681
What a gentleman you are.

145
00:06:21,081 --> 00:06:23,081
We had a big meal earlier.

146
00:06:23,511 --> 00:06:24,681
What makes you think so?

147
00:06:24,951 --> 00:06:27,150
- What?
- I don't think we did.

148
00:06:27,151 --> 00:06:28,590
I actually prefer it this way.

149
00:06:28,591 --> 00:06:29,891
- What?
- I prefer it this way.

150
00:06:30,051 --> 00:06:31,560
A foodie is my ideal type.

151
00:06:31,561 --> 00:06:32,721
- For real?
- I'm serious.

152
00:06:35,661 --> 00:06:37,901
Then she's totally your ideal type.

153
00:06:38,361 --> 00:06:39,631
There's nothing to worry about.

154
00:06:39,861 --> 00:06:41,870
I bet Hoo said that knowing it.

155
00:06:41,871 --> 00:06:42,931
(Remark meant for Yu Bin)

156
00:06:43,201 --> 00:06:44,521
- Here's your order.
- Thank you.

157
00:06:44,571 --> 00:06:45,600
How's the meal?

158
00:06:45,601 --> 00:06:46,671
- Good.
- It's delicious.

159
00:06:47,311 --> 00:06:49,310
If you want these but can't finish the others,

160
00:06:49,311 --> 00:06:51,011
- put them back on the plate.
- Got it.

161
00:06:51,441 --> 00:06:53,781
(The main dish is served.)

162
00:06:53,851 --> 00:06:55,780
- Yu Bin loves that.
- It looks amazing.

163
00:06:55,781 --> 00:06:57,280
- Eating nonstop.
- Yes.

164
00:06:57,281 --> 00:06:58,320
- Without a break.
- Thank you.

165
00:06:58,321 --> 00:06:59,321
I see.

166
00:06:59,322 --> 00:07:00,550
It's a feast right here.

167
00:07:00,551 --> 00:07:02,221
(The table is full of food.)

168
00:07:02,691 --> 00:07:04,121
(Digging in)

169
00:07:06,491 --> 00:07:08,361
(Digging in)

170
00:07:10,091 --> 00:07:11,430
- It's the same.
- This one's good.

171
00:07:11,431 --> 00:07:12,501
- Is it?
- Yes.

172
00:07:16,601 --> 00:07:20,711
(Just like a foodie would, Yu Bin is digging in.)

173
00:07:21,141 --> 00:07:22,471
(Laughing)

174
00:07:22,911 --> 00:07:24,611
- Why are you laughing? Am I funny?
- No.

175
00:07:24,641 --> 00:07:25,681
You're cute.

176
00:07:29,181 --> 00:07:32,521
(The born chubbies' delicious meal date)

177
00:07:34,921 --> 00:07:36,951
You look great right now. Let me take a photo.

178
00:07:39,291 --> 00:07:41,291
- My lipstick must've worn off.
- Oh, my.

179
00:07:42,561 --> 00:07:44,461
My lips must look pale right now.

180
00:07:46,761 --> 00:07:47,771
Stay still.

181
00:07:48,571 --> 00:07:49,571
(Shocked)

182
00:07:53,041 --> 00:07:56,270
- He's got a good shot.
- She's looking gorgeous.

183
00:07:56,271 --> 00:07:58,781
Such a reaction is important.

184
00:07:59,241 --> 00:08:01,251
He's the perfect boyfriend.

185
00:08:07,691 --> 00:08:08,751
I'm getting shy.

186
00:08:10,561 --> 00:08:12,790
(Yoon Hoo, Yu Bin's exclusive photographer)

187
00:08:12,791 --> 00:08:14,931
The photos are turning out great.

188
00:08:17,261 --> 00:08:19,230
She must've posed for them.

189
00:08:19,231 --> 00:08:20,831
- Such a pose is rare.
- Nice.

190
00:08:21,971 --> 00:08:23,500
- Nice one.
- Like, "Great!"

191
00:08:23,501 --> 00:08:24,671
- He did a good job.
- Yes.

192
00:08:27,311 --> 00:08:28,511
Eat already.

193
00:08:29,541 --> 00:08:31,411
They're turning out great.

194
00:08:32,241 --> 00:08:33,580
Hoo is full...

195
00:08:33,581 --> 00:08:34,981
- even without the food.
- Exactly.

196
00:08:36,411 --> 00:08:37,451
Eat already.

197
00:08:38,881 --> 00:08:41,091
During the meal,

198
00:08:41,321 --> 00:08:43,520
Hoo suddenly said the lighting was great...

199
00:08:43,521 --> 00:08:45,261
