200
00:08:45,921 --> 00:08:49,231
He took them with great reactions,

201
00:08:49,891 --> 00:08:51,001
and that made me happy.

202
00:08:51,231 --> 00:08:55,570
As I thought, I felt the most relaxed...

203
00:08:55,571 --> 00:08:57,201
and had the most fun with Hoo.

204
00:08:59,801 --> 00:09:01,640
This couple gives off a sense of stability.

205
00:09:01,641 --> 00:09:02,670
- Exactly.
- Yes.

206
00:09:02,671 --> 00:09:04,040
- It's a date.
- Yes.

207
00:09:04,041 --> 00:09:05,210
A real date.

208
00:09:05,211 --> 00:09:06,481
(Like a new couple)

209
00:09:07,311 --> 00:09:10,621
(Last 1-on-1 Date: Shin Jae Hyuk and Woo Seo Yoon)

210
00:09:11,581 --> 00:09:15,621
(A ski resort full of winter vibes)

211
00:09:24,961 --> 00:09:26,031
I'm nervous.

212
00:09:28,531 --> 00:09:29,571
To think we'd come...

213
00:09:30,601 --> 00:09:32,571
- to a ski resort.
- I know, right?

214
00:09:33,741 --> 00:09:35,870
- Finally.
- These two kids...

215
00:09:35,871 --> 00:09:38,480
- Goodness.
- are the highlight.

216
00:09:38,481 --> 00:09:40,850
Physical contact is natural at ski resorts.

217
00:09:40,851 --> 00:09:43,051
- Totally.
- Ski resorts are like that.

218
00:09:43,111 --> 00:09:45,381
- Physical contact is unavoidable.
- Yes.

219
00:09:45,421 --> 00:09:47,690
- Remember the movie "Love Story?" - Yes.

220
00:09:47,691 --> 00:09:48,820
You end up rolling in the snowfield.

221
00:09:48,821 --> 00:09:50,190
- Exactly.
- Yes.

222
00:09:50,191 --> 00:09:51,260
Right?

223
00:09:51,261 --> 00:09:53,061
(What's their date going to be like?)

224
00:09:53,491 --> 00:09:55,030
(Are you good at skiing?)

225
00:09:55,031 --> 00:09:57,631
I've been skiing and snowboarding for over ten years.

226
00:09:58,331 --> 00:10:00,100
When I go to ski resorts every winter,

227
00:10:00,101 --> 00:10:01,261
I enjoy it to the point of...

228
00:10:01,431 --> 00:10:04,341
skiing and snowboarding all the way from the top.

229
00:10:04,971 --> 00:10:06,571
Eun Byul also skis, you know?

230
00:10:08,241 --> 00:10:09,740
(What did you think about the ski resort date?)

231
00:10:09,741 --> 00:10:11,411
I got so scared.

232
00:10:11,811 --> 00:10:13,380
On our way there,

233
00:10:13,381 --> 00:10:15,751
I was excited.

234
00:10:16,011 --> 00:10:18,620
But when we arrived at the ski resort,

235
00:10:18,621 --> 00:10:21,021
I got really nervous and scared.

236
00:10:21,421 --> 00:10:23,621
(Seo Yoon is unfamiliar with ski resorts.)

237
00:10:24,361 --> 00:10:26,791
- Safety is first.
- Yes, safety.

238
00:10:27,561 --> 00:10:28,591
Don't get hurt.

239
00:10:30,031 --> 00:10:31,951
When was the last time you came to a ski resort?

240
00:10:34,271 --> 00:10:36,131
- Middle school.
- Middle school?

241
00:10:37,341 --> 00:10:40,141
(Struggling)

242
00:10:40,341 --> 00:10:41,640
(Glancing)

243
00:10:41,641 --> 00:10:42,671
It's heavy, right?

244
00:10:42,841 --> 00:10:44,380
- Let me.
- No, it's okay.

245
00:10:44,381 --> 00:10:46,510
It feels lighter if you hold it like this.

246
00:10:46,511 --> 00:10:47,581
Okay then.

247
00:10:48,451 --> 00:10:50,850
That's it. Jae Hyuk is a gentleman.

248
00:10:50,851 --> 00:10:51,851
Thanks.

249
00:10:53,321 --> 00:10:54,420
- Are you okay?
- Yes.

250
00:10:54,421 --> 00:10:56,491
- I'm just dragging them.
- Is that so?

251
00:10:58,321 --> 00:10:59,681
It's your first time snowboarding,

252
00:10:59,721 --> 00:11:00,930
- Yes, a total first.
- right?

253
00:11:00,931 --> 00:11:01,960
A total first?

254
00:11:01,961 --> 00:11:03,531
But I've always wanted to snowboard.

255
00:11:04,731 --> 00:11:06,800
- I might frustrate you.
- No way.

256
00:11:06,801 --> 00:11:07,971
Apologies in advance.

257
00:11:08,371 --> 00:11:09,701
I'll try...

258
00:11:10,601 --> 00:11:13,740
my best so that you don't get hurt.

